name: Warrior Nurse
description:
This is an old school style  scroller.

Your Objective is to collect 1500 points.

You are a Warrior Nurse who lives surrounded by deadly diseases. 

You try not to be hit by the ailments and you try to gather the 1500 points before your stamina runs out.

This game was made for the 

Support Indie 2020 Game Jam

With Theme Progress makes you weaker.

The music we have was made by  Ugly Wormz Music. (https://assetstore.unity.com/publishers/37454)

Thank you for Supporting us
